### Create actu (multipart with optional image)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/actus
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=---011000010111000001101001

---011000010111000001101001
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="titre"

Nouvelle actu
---011000010111000001101001
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contenu"

Contenu de l'actualité
---011000010111000001101001
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./fixtures/cover.jpg
---011000010111000001101001--

### Update actu (multipart with optional image)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/admin/actus/{{actuId}}
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=---011000010111000001101001

---011000010111000001101001
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="titre"

Titre mis à jour
---011000010111000001101001
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="new-cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./fixtures/new-cover.jpg
---011000010111000001101001--

### Delete actu
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/admin/actus/{{actuId}}
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Get all actus
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/actus
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Get single actu
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/actus/{{actuId}}
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
